OL,3,CWoman in court in connection with
OL,4,Cfatal XL bully dog attack in Bristol
OL,6,FA woman has appeared in court charged
OL,7,Fover a dog attack involving an XL
OL,8,Fbully dog in which a teenager died.
OL,10,FKelcie Reed, 24, attended Bristol
OL,11,FMagistrates' Court accused of being in
OL,12,Fcharge of a dog dangerously out of
OL,13,Fcontrol, causing injury resulting in
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FIt is alleged that the dog, an XL
OL,17,Fbully named Prince, fatally injured
OL,18,FMorgan Dorsett, 19, inside a flat at
OL,19,FCobhorn Drive, Withywood, Bristol, on
OL,20,FFebruary 26 last year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
