OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777039866
OL,3,CWoman in court in connection with
OL,4,Cfatal XL bully dog attack in Bristol
OL,6,FMs Dorsett suffered fatal bites to her
OL,7,Fneck during the incident. The dog was
OL,8,Fput down afterwards.
OL,10,FReed, of Lawrence Weston, Bristol,
OL,11,Fwept as the charge was read to her by
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Lynne Matthews on
OL,13,FThursday morning (April 23).
OL,15,FShe did not enter a plea to the charge
OL,16,Fagainst her and the case was adjourned
OL,17,Fto Bristol Crown Court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
