PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777039866
OL,3,CWoman in court in connection with
OL,4,Cfatal XL bully dog attack in Bristol
OL,6,FThe judge said: "I send you now to the
OL,7,Fcrown court at Bristol where you must
OL,8,Fappear on May 27. Between now and
OL,9,Fthen, you are on conditional bail."
OL,11,FThe bail conditions state that Reed
OL,12,Fmust not own or be in control of any
OL,13,Fdog, under any circumstances.
OL,15,FReed will next appear before Bristol
OL,16,FCrown Court on May 27.
